| `rd` | `[11:7]` | – |
| `funct3` | `[14:12]` | – |
| `rs1` | `[19:15]` | – |
| `rs2` | `[24:20]` | – |
| `funct7` | `[31:25]` | – |
| `imm` | – | See the table above for each format |

